<p>How can i get the dynamic width of <code>LinearLayout</code> at runtime?</p>  <p>I mean, i want to get the width of <code>LinearLayout</code> at runtime , when <code>LinearLayout</code> visibility is <code>"GONE"</code> and <code>LinearLayout</code> width is <code>"match_parent"</code> in xml layout file. </p>  <p>I can get width using <code>onGlobalLayoutChangeListener</code> and <code>onPreDrawListener</code> but only if our view(LinearLayout) is already "<code>VISIBLE"</code> state, not at <code>"GONE"</code> state. </p>  <p>Is here any solution for this problem? </p>  <p>Thank you so much for your time.  </p>